{"tid":1286550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得唔好搞武漢嘅入","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T03:07:32.000Z","uid":4419,"like":33,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"ff15e51e79b8d40980108feef748a64aed876549","tid":1286550,"uid":4419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"第一，搞武漢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不等於</span></span>建設民主中國。就係因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HK IS NOT CHINA</span></span>所以更加應該搞到中國分化內鬥從而分裂，對香港完全無壞。如果認為要同中國劃清界線所以放棄打到佢仆街嘅機會未免太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，五大訴求都未爭取到你好得閒？我敢反問一句 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你好撚忙？</span></span>依家係咪日日有五大訴求有關嘅行動先？我地嘅目光要放遠啲，全面打低共產黨，各省獨立，香港獨立etc<br />\n<br />\n 再者，又話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各有各做？</span></span> 連打網戰聲援都唔撚比？"},{"pid":"cd74e4e55ff5443e2bc249592240324a59215d5e","tid":1286550,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dccc78379b23c01ffaa66dde090f9af7dfcfd3e5","tid":1286550,"uid":148987,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"武漢人：港獨分子唔好諗住利用我地<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好自作多情<br />\n<br />\n要撐就撐分離主義滬獨川獨疆獨圖獨台獨<br />\n<br />\n集中五大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令